      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented modeling protocol reviewed by independent analyst; boundary conditions and loading confirmed against ASTM F1717 specification.",
      "rationale": "Modeling protocol reviewed by a second FEA engineer not involved in model construction. Boundary conditions (fixed lower grip, displacement-controlled upper grip at 1 mm/min equivalent) and loading axis confirmed against ASTM F1717-15 Section 7. No use errors identified."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Physics captured by model form justified relative to dominant deformation mechanisms observed experimentally.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic with nonlinear contact (Lagrange multiplier) and bilinear isotropic hardening plasticity for titanium alloy. Dominant mechanisms are elastic bending of rod, plastic hinge formation at screw-rod interface, and contact at polyethylene block. Model form captures all three mechanisms as confirmed by experimental strain gauge data."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric inputs sourced from traceable measurements or published standards; uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V material properties (E=114 GPa, yield 880 MPa, UTS 950 MPa) sourced from ASTM F136 and confirmed by coupon tensile testing of lot-matched material. Geometric inputs from CMM measurements of production components. Input uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (N=1000 samples); combined uncertainty reported as uval."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
