      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions span clinically relevant range or multiple loading configurations evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 compression-bending configuration only. Torsion and tension-bending configurations not evaluated in this COU. This factor is below the required level; the limitation is accepted because the COU is scoped to compression-bending only and the decision consequence is Medium."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
