      "rationale": "Validation uses identical non-cannulated 7.5 mm production screws, identical rod diameter and alloy, and identical ASTM F1717 fixture geometry as the COU. Loading rate equivalency between quasi-static FEA and 1 mm/min experimental rate confirmed by strain-rate sensitivity analysis showing <0.3% QoI change."
